      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 8 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 8 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六，有孚，比之，无咎。有孚盈缶，終來有它，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject seeking by his sincerity to win the attachment of his object. There will be no error. Let (the breast) be full of sincerity as an earthenware vessel is of its contents, and it will in the end bring other advantages.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
