      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 8 六二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六二，比之自內，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the second SIX, divided, we see the movement towards union and attachment proceeding from the inward (mind). With firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
