      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三，比之匪人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the third SIX, divided, we see its subject seeking for union with such as ought not to be associated with.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
