      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六四，外比之，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the fourth SIX, divided, we see its subject seeking for union with the one beyond himself. With firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
