      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 8 上六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上六，比之无首，凶。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the topmost SIX, divided, we see one seeking union and attachment without having taken the first step (to such an end). There will be evil.</seg>
      </tuv>
